      "patchset_number": 4,
      "line": 62,
      "message": "I dont think it make any sense to create \"our own marker interface\" as currently legacy events that are auto-generated from json schema implements Serializable. Anyway in near future legacy events would be removed, we should not waste our time in after effects here.",
